%% Diagram: Troubleshooting Decision Tree
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false, 'flowchart': {'htmlLabels': false}}}%%
flowchart TB
    problem{What's wrong?} -->|Empty render| syntax_fix[Check source syntax<br/>Validate at mermaid.live]
    problem -->|Chromium not found| warmup_fix[Run npx diagramkit warmup]
    problem -->|sharp error| sharp_fix[Run npm add sharp]
    problem -->|Manifest stale| manifest_fix["Run --force or<br/>delete manifest.json"]
    problem -->|Dark colors wrong| contrast_fix["Try --no-contrast<br/>Use neutral fills"]
    problem -->|Watch not detecting| watch_fix[Check extensions<br/>Avoid node_modules]
    problem -->|CI hangs| dispose_fix["Call dispose() or<br/>use one-shot render"]
    problem -->|Out of memory| memory_fix["Lower --scale"]
